{"tid":1062180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[洋腸] 六旬婦網上識洋漢遇騙失115萬元 警拘中年女子","createTime":"2019-03-15T02:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T11:51:47.000Z","uid":56881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c619c11b2a445dacc3b554ed226d5d9ab4949c01","tid":1062180,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%98%E6%B4%8B%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%87%E9%A8%99%E5%A4%B1115%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90-081200178.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%25B4%258B%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2581%2587%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25A4%25B1115%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590-081200178.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=d2d5745d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%98%E6%B4%8B%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%87%E9%A8%99%E5%A4%B1115%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90-081200178.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】警方於1月上旬接獲<span style=\"color: red;\">一名65歲姓陳本地女子報案，指她通過社交媒體結識一名外籍男子，該名男子表示有禮物從外地寄到香港</span>，要求受害人存錢至多個指定的本地銀行戶口，以繳交關稅。受害人按其指示，於2018年3月至12月期間多次轉帳後，未能聯絡上該名男子，懷疑受騙，遂報案。案中損失金額約115萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n警員經調查後，於1月9日在荃灣區拘捕一名53歲姓陳本地女子，涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」。案件由中區警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。被捕女子已獲准保釋候查，須於4月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港女食洋腸真係無分老幼"},{"pid":"8d69050701c2b30dbbc426602f14c6abf407c0f8","tid":1062180,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1051136/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1051136/page/1</a><br />\n即刻諗起"},{"pid":"ea9318fc325d92c45739cb8e19e9a11977362eab","tid":1062180,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"香港女人真係好恨洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}